aboutPage.introduction: Hi, my name is Joana, and I'm based in Portugal. I'm a Frontend developer with a passion for creating useful tools and pages that help make people's lives easier. Most of my experience is with the Angular framework, but I love exploring new technologies and tools. With a background in Engineering Physics, curiosity and problem-solving are part of who I am.
